---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our History" description="Explore the journey of MakerFriends from a small garage project to a global maker community.">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="flex-1">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 text-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">Our Journey</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          From humble beginnings to a global community of makers
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-gray-900">MakerFriends Timeline</h2>
        
        <!-- Timeline Item 2018 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-blue-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2018</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">The Spark of an Idea üí°</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              It all started in a small garage in Portland, Oregon. Five friends‚Äîan engineer, a teacher, 
              a designer, a student, and a woodworker‚Äîbegan meeting weekly to work on projects and share 
              ideas. They quickly realized the magic that happens when makers collaborate and support each other.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2019 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-purple-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-purple-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2019</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Going Digital üåê</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              The garage group launched the first version of MakerFriends.com as a simple blog to share 
              their projects. Within months, makers from around the city started contributing their own 
              creations. The community had begun to grow beyond our wildest dreams.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2020 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-pink-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-pink-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-pink-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2020</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Connecting Through Crisis ü§ù</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              When the pandemic hit, our community came together like never before. Virtual workshops, 
              online maker meetups, and collaborative projects helped makers stay connected and creative 
              during challenging times. We grew from 200 to over 1,000 members.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2021 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-green-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2021</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Education Initiative üéì</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We launched our STEM/STEAM education program, partnering with schools and libraries to 
              bring maker education to students. Over 50 educational institutions joined our program, 
              inspiring the next generation of innovators.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2022 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-amber-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-amber-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-amber-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2022</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Global Expansion üåç</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              MakerFriends went global! Makers from every continent joined our community. We hosted our 
              first international Maker Fair with participants from 30 countries, showcasing the universal 
              language of creativity and innovation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2023 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-indigo-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2023</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Platform Revolution üöÄ</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We completely rebuilt our platform with cutting-edge technology, adding features like 
              project collaboration tools, advanced search, skill-based matching, and a comprehensive 
              maker directory. Our community surpassed 3,000 active makers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2024 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-12 border-l-4 border-red-500">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-500 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-red-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2024</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">Innovation Grants Program üí∞</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We launched our Innovation Grants Program, providing funding and resources to makers with 
              groundbreaking ideas. We supported 100+ projects in categories ranging from sustainable 
              technology to educational tools.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Timeline Item 2025 -->
        <div class="relative pl-8">
          <div class="absolute -left-4 top-0 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-full border-4 border-white"></div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <div class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">2025 - Today</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3 text-gray-900">The Future is Bright ‚ú®</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Today, MakerFriends is a thriving community of over 5,000 makers across 50+ countries. 
              We've shared over 12,000 projects, hosted hundreds of workshops, and built countless 
              friendships. But we're just getting started!
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold">
              Join us as we continue to innovate, create, and inspire the makers of tomorrow.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Milestones -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">Key Milestones</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-2">5,000+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Active Makers</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-2">12,000+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Projects Shared</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-pink-600 mb-2">50+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Countries</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">500+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium">Events Hosted</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Founders Section -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900">Meet Our Founders</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold">
              JD
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Jamie Davis</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Engineer & Innovator</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-purple-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold">
              SM
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Sarah Martinez</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">STEM Educator</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-pink-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold">
              AC
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Alex Chen</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Creative Designer</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold">
              TK
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Taylor Kim</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">CS Student</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-amber-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-3xl font-bold">
              RJ
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Riley Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Master Woodworker</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">Be Part of Our Next Chapter</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Every great maker was once a beginner. Join our community and write your own maker story!
        </p>
        <a href="/signup" class="inline-block px-10 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 text-white rounded-full font-bold text-xl hover:shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105">
          Start Your Journey Today üöÄ
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

